\fs36 \cf0 1. Overview\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 This project merges a "Living World Engine" with autonomous AI characters and an "Observer Mode" with a more traditional top-down RPG featuring direct player control, combat, and progression. The goal is to create a dynamic world where players can observe AI life and then seamlessly jump in to participate in adventures. The game runs entirely in the browser using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript (ES6 Modules), with no external dependencies or servers required for the core engine.\
